author: Ron Higgins, NOLA.com | The Times-Picayune
title: Let's talk Fournette, national and SEC title chases today at 1 p.m. with LSU/SEC columnist Ron Higgins
text:
Are teams playing dirty against Leonard Fournette?
What will it take for LSU to stay unbeaten and have a shot at the national championship?
Is the West a two-team race between the Tigers and Alabama, or could it get crazy?
Who's the best team in the East?
Join me here at 1 p.m. to discuss these topics and more. Digest that lunch and join in!
